    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been pampered since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that remains entirely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections, this car looks as though it just rolled off the assembly line. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather seats show zero wear, and the cabin still retains that distinct new-car scent. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete folder of records to prove its pedigree. It has been strictly garage-kept under a soft cover and has never seen rain or inclement weather. From the spotless engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key experience, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
